{"tid":1709844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唉屌，會唔會攪到日日都要行路軌番工架...","createTime":"2019-11-12T04:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T14:56:55.000Z","uid":183991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b1a39fb00d4350a1ce9c6381c8e562684b551280","tid":1709844,"uid":183991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RcPZNZ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcPZNZ3.png&h=975872af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Br9ySrL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBr9ySrL.png&h=acf7270c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kJZqEVoMUYQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkJZqEVoMUYQ&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=7bc70a7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kJZqEVoMUYQ</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪有咩密閉恐懼症，架車一停一陣就好驚好想爆窗出去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好用黎爆港島站啲大玻璃，巴士大銀幕，如果多人爆晒車啲玻璃都好危險，隨時又無車番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好狗鐵巴士一次過攪，林奠媽媽今日先讚完我番工好尊敬我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6064d0a4631783e8611e39dae58f5f587d95012","tid":1709844,"uid":183991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:01:29.000Z","msg":"我想番工x1"},{"pid":"50ba08232380e3f11aef9f8cd2736238fa84bfe5","tid":1709844,"uid":183991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:01:41.000Z","msg":"我想番工x2"},{"pid":"bb6cc0ef0951ba23494a0a4393426790cf3f32d9","tid":1709844,"uid":183991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:01:53.000Z","msg":"我想番工x3"},{"pid":"b71dd014b2c16fe8d6043f4165e455b31652d739","tid":1709844,"uid":183991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:02:07.000Z","msg":"我想番工x4"},{"pid":"46bf066c980d342799b2b9826df489428516